e going to feel,\\\" said Annie Heffernon, vice president of the women's program at USA Gymnastics,told theWashington Post.\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 510, \"end\": 515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Awards\", \"score\": 0.9999999947581273, \"rank\": 4.118056905003983e-09, \"text\": \"Annie\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Annie_Awards\"}, {\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.461038583932981e-12, \"text\": \"USA Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moments\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 394}, {\"ngram\": \"especially the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"every four years\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 470}, {\"ngram\": \"vice president\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 541}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's program\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 564}, {\"ngram\": \"theWashington Post\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Regardless of their performance, I want them to feel amazing and beautiful when they go out and represent the U.S. in a leotard that they can be proud of.\\\"\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their performance\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 640}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"a leotard\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Designed and produced by Reading, Pennsylvania-based apparel company GK Elite, the leotards have up to10,000 crystalsapplied in intricate patterns to custom fabric.\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reading\", \"score\": 0.9719227525373398, \"rank\": 0.028887831995918285, \"text\": \"Reading\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reading\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reading\"}, {\"begin\": 835, \"end\": 837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"score\": 0.9999996446677591, \"rank\": 2.551050535060275e-07, \"text\": \"GK\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Field_hockey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the leotards\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"intricate patterns\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"custom fabric\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The red, white, and blue color scheme is an obvious nod to the competitors' nationality, but the ornate pattern of the crystals-as well as the unmistakable glow emanating from them-is a nod to Paris' nickname of the City of Lights.\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1124, \"end\": 1129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.943721989326151e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The red, white, and blue color scheme\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"an obvious nod\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitors' nationality\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"the ornate pattern\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"the crystals\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"the unmistakable glow emanating\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"a nod\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"Lights\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bright designs follow a convention of Olympic gymnasts donning themselves with ornamented uniforms, a trend that has increased in intensity since 2008 when gold medalist Nastia Liukin's leotard hadonly 184 crystalson it.\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bright designs\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1181}, {\"ngram\": \"a convention\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic gymnasts\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"ornamented uniforms\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"a trend\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1274}, {\"ngram\": \"intensity\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The uniforms may be visually difficult to miss, but it's the athletes who have garnered spectators' attention.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The uniforms\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators' attention\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A peak of 8.2 million viewers watched gymnast Simone Biles secure her spot in the U.S. Olympic gymnastics team last month,among the highestratings of this year's U.S. trials.\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A peak\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1506}, {\"ngram\": \"8.2 million viewers\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1529}, {\"ngram\": \"her spot\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. Olympic gymnastics team\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"the highestratings\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's U.S. trials\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1673}]}, {\"sentenc